===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈtɛpɪd/}}
* {{audio|en-us-tepid.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# [[lukewarm|Lukewarm]]; neither [[warm]] nor [[cool]].
#: ''I'm drinking a cup of '''tepid''' water.''
# [[uninterested|Uninterested]]; exhibiting little passion or eagerness.
#: ''He gave me a '''tepid''' response to the proposal.''

